{"tid":1695329,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HKmap.live嘅手足團隊，麻煩入入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-05T14:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T15:37:58.000Z","uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f8efc332c6f766a50a176682d900f3b02f1b244","tid":1695329,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:40:38.000Z","msg":"相信大家都知道個map係幾好用<br />\n有樣想團隊會諗到辦法跟進<br />\n就係當不停有新料更新（例如2豬由A point &gt; B point）<br />\n出現以下情況 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.成張map啲icon會重覆，好難睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.唔知每個報料嘅路線</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n諗到個idea<br />\n每一個新報料可以選擇<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">連結</span></span>到已有嘅報料<br />\n即係咁<br />\n2200 X 報左A point有狗車正駛向 B point\b<br />\n2210 Y 報狗車已到B point<br />\nY 報料嘅時候可以link到相關嘅情報   <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">顯示整條死狗路線方向</span></span><br />\n同時 舊有嘅報料可以透明顯示    <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">令整張map更簡潔更好睇 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/utinCLC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FutinCLC.png&h=61c215e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb7e2ee8e78df6058098b74ff38b975c362dcb09","tid":1695329,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"幫忙前線嘅一大工具<br />\n自推 1／10"},{"pid":"49f8a4f500634a5f9189764483b70054b94a0af7","tid":1695329,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"幫忙前線嘅一大工具<br />\n自推 2／10"},{"pid":"7b3558558f696690923936ee7dedc530dc8c3a55","tid":1695329,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:52:57.000Z","msg":"其實有無可能D狗或三毛玩報假消息?<br />\n我見元朗果度而家好似打到仆街<br />\n但又無一個live影緊<br />\n會唔會其實係引緊手足去俾黑警圍捕?"},{"pid":"7c1ff